<br>
I petitioned and sent e-mails to Zrinic and Jill Henderson (JHenderson@station.sony.com), who is the CSR lead, and they were able to verify in the logs that my corpse decayed prematurely, and they arranged a time for me to meet with Zrinic online and have my character restored from a backup prior to the corpse loss.  Thankfully I lost nothing, and actually came back with more XP than I died with, because I had an unrezzed death between my backup time and when my corpse vanished.<br>
<br>
Be polite, but insistent, and I'm sure that Zrinic will be able to help you.  I was ready to finally throw in the towel on EQ for the couple days it took to get in touch with Zrinic, but patience definitely paid off.<br>
<br>
Good luck!<br>
