se rotting rules, its posted and written in same place where the 24 hour online and 7day offline rule is at (help file AND vi site) it by no means is hidden.<br>
<br>
Its a tad outdated because this was before the 3 minute empty corpse poof was removed.<br>
<br>
----<br>
Level 1 - 5:&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 30 minutes<br>
Level 6+: &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp 24 hours of online time, or 1 week of offline time, whichever comes first.<br>
<br>
*Note:  If you have no items on your corpse, it will decay in 3 minutes regardless of level.  It is best advised to get your corpse right away.  If that is not possible, remember that one-hour in game is the same as seven hours out of game.  Also, be advised that your corpse decay is still advancing if you leave your computer at the character select screen or play on another character on that same account.<br>
